Global Scrap Aluminium Recycling Market Insights
Scrap Aluminium Recycling Market size was valued at USD 84 Billion in 2022 and is projected to reach USD 112 Billion by 2030, growing at a CAGR of 4.1% from 2024 to 2030.

Scrap Aluminium Recycling Market Overview
The global aluminum scrap recycling market was valued at approximately $50 billion in 2022 and is projected to reach about $80 billion by 2030, growing at a compound annual growth rate (CAGR) of around 6.5%. This growth is driven by the increasing demand for sustainable practices and the economic value of recycled materials. Aluminum is one of the most recyclable metals, and its scrap recycling not only conserves energy—up to 95% less energy is required to recycle aluminum compared to producing it from raw materials—but also significantly reduces greenhouse gas emissions.

